#: ../../docs/classes/class_audiostream.rst:21
msgid ""
"Base class for audio streams. Audio streams are used for sound effects "
"and music playback, and support WAV (via :ref:`AudioStreamSample "
"<class_AudioStreamSample>`) and OGG (via :ref:`AudioStreamOGGVorbis "
"<class_AudioStreamOGGVorbis>`) file formats."
msgstr ""
"音频流的基类。音频流用于声音效果和音乐播放，并支持WAV（通过 :ref:`AudioStreamSample "
"<class_AudioStreamSample>`）和OGG（通过 :ref:`AudioStreamOGGVorbis "
"<class_AudioStreamOGGVorbis>`）文件格式。"

